    ]}
    image={{
      src: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581092160562-40aa08e78837?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2070&q=80',
      alt: 'Proyectos de Ingeniería',
    }}
    callToAction={{
      target: '_blank',
      text: 'See Projects',
      icon: 'tabler:chevron-right',
      href: '/projects#engineering',
    }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="content">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-3xl mb-2">
        Engineering & Hardware Design
      </h3>
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="bg">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-transparent"></div>
    </Fragment>
  </Content>

  <!-- Steps Widget ****************** -->
  <Steps
    id="resume"
    title="Work experience"
    items={[
  {
    title:
    'Freelance Professional Engineer<br />  <span class="text-sm font-normal">2022 - PRESENT</span>',
    // description: `Asistió a diseñadores senior en la creación de conceptos de diseño y activos visuales. <br /> Contribuyó al desarrollo de identidades de marca y material de marketing. <br /> Colaboró con el equipo de marketing para asegurar un diseño consistente en las campañas. <br /> Adquirió experiencia práctica en varios programas y herramientas de diseño.`,
    description: 'Professional freelance engineer with extensive experience delivering high-quality projects on platforms like Fiverr. I have completed numerous projects spanning web development, electronic schematic and PCB design, CAD modeling and simulation, and web design. With a commitment to precision and innovation, I tailor each project to meet client specifications, leveraging my interdisciplinary expertise to provide effective solutions across both software and hardware domains.',
    icon: 'tabler:briefcase',
  },
  {
    title:
      'Frontend Software Engineer <br /> <span class="font-normal">Unydos Consulting S.A.S, COL</span> <br /> <span class="text-sm font-normal">2024</span>',
    description: "As a lead developer on a legacy software modernization project, I was responsible for transforming an existing software application into a modern, scalable solution using React. My role involved translating client requirements into actionable technical tasks, which I delegated to the development team to ensure efficient and accurate execution. By overseeing the technical direction of the project and aligning development efforts with the client's needs, I helped drive the evolution of this application into a responsive, user-centric product that meets current industry standards.",
    icon: 'tabler:code',
  },
  {
    title:
      'CAD Mechanical Engineer <br /> <span class="font-normal">Industrial Sector (Multiple Employers)</span> <br /> <span class="text-sm font-normal">2016 - 2022</span>',
    description: "As a Mechanical Designer specializing in industrial solutions, I collaborated directly with clients—primarily within diverse industries—to analyze their requirements and provide customized engineering solutions. My role involved on-site assessments to obtain accurate measurements and understand the unique needs of each project. Through conceptual, basic, and detailed engineering, I designed solutions such as tanks, pipes, conveyor systems, elevators, and platforms, each intended to improve and optimize industrial processes. My expertise lies in creating functional and efficient designs that enhance production lines and align with the client's operational objectives.",
    icon: 'tabler:settings',
  }
]}
    classes={{ container: 'max-w-3xl' }}
  />

  <Features3
    title="Skills"
    subtitle="Discover the skills that allow me to bring imagination to life through design."
    columns={3}
    defaultIcon="tabler:point-filled"
    items={[
  {
    title: 'Frontend Web Development',
    description: 'Specializing in building dynamic and responsive user interfaces with React, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, focusing on creating fluid and interactive user experiences.',
  },
  {
    title: 'CAD Modeling and Simulation',
    description: 'Proficient in the use of CAD software for 3D modeling and simulation of mechanical components, from conceptual design to detailed engineering analysis.',
  },
  {
    title: 'PCB and Electronics Design',
    description: 'Design and simulation of electronic circuits and PCBs, ensuring optimal performance and integration for a variety of hardware projects.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Embedded Systems and Microcontrollers',
    description: 'Programming and integrating Arduino, ESP32, and other microcontrollers to develop efficient and reliable hardware solutions.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Robotics and Control Systems',
    description: 'Development and simulation of robotic systems using MATLAB and LabVIEW for precise control, automation, and data analysis.',
  },
  {
    title: 'HMI Interface Development',
    description: 'Creating intuitive graphical interfaces for HMI devices, including Raspberry Pi touchscreens and microcontroller displays, to improve user interaction and control.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Problem Solving and Optimization',
    description: 'Ability to analyze complex problems and develop creative and effective solutions that improve performance, reduce costs, and increase productivity.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Project Leadership and Team Collaboration',
    description: 'Leading projects from conception to execution, coordinating teams, delegating tasks, and ensuring alignment with client requirements and deadlines.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Technical Communication and Customer Relations',
    description: 'Strong communication skills to translate technical requirements into actionable tasks, maintaining clear and efficient dialogue with clients to ensure project success.',
  },
]}
  />


